[Category "Basic Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "basic_bidding/major_suit_openings"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

With 6 points you must respond and you should let partner know you have support for his suit. So you bid 2\H and he promptly raises to 4\H. It's a good thing he had 20 points isn't it.}

